import './index.scss' const About = () => { return (

It's nice to meet you!

I recently graduated from Oregon State University with a Bachelor's Degree in Computer Science with a minor in Business Administration. I am actively seeking professional opportunities in software engineering.

My time at Oregon State provided me with ample experience in many development fields. I currently find myself most interested and experienced with full stack web development but am open to new opportunites.

My current plan going forward is to familiarize myself with the professional software engineering environment to gear myself to become a project manager or scrum master in the near future. I believe my development knowledge combined with my communication skills place me in a unique position to lead.

As a new graduate I am extremely excited to get to work and make professional connections! Please feel free to get in contact with me through my contact page or on LinkedIn.

) } export default About;
